---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Small Air Purifier for Desk 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of desktop air purifiers. Clean the air in your immediate workspace.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} articleSchema={{headline: pageTitle, description: pageDescription, datePublished: '2026-05', authorName: 'Toolwise Team'}} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Small Air Purifier for Desk</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · HEPA Filter</div>

      <p>Clean air in your immediate workspace can improve focus and reduce allergies. After testing multiple desktop air purifiers, one stands out for its effective HEPA filtration, quiet operation, and compact design that fits perfectly on any desk.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 Levoit Core Mini Air Purifier</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>HEPA filter captures 99.97% of particles</strong> — effective air cleaning</li>
          <li><strong>3 fan speeds with whisper-quiet sleep mode</strong> — won't disturb work</li>
          <li><strong>Covers 178 sq ft — perfect for offices</strong> — ideal room coverage</li>
          <li><strong>Aromatherapy pad for essential oils</strong> — optional fragrance</li>
          <li><strong>Energy efficient at only 7W power draw</strong> — low operating cost</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=levoit+mini+air+purifier&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it wins at this price</h3>
      <p>Most desktop air purifiers are either too loud or don't have true HEPA filtration. The Levoit Core Mini uses a 3-stage filtration system with a true HEPA filter that captures 99.97% of particles. The whisper-quiet sleep mode won't disturb your work or sleep.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Office workers, allergy sufferers, and anyone who wants cleaner air in their immediate workspace. It's perfect for small offices, dorm rooms, and bedrooms where you spend a lot of time.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>